<TEXT>
marion barrys lawyer is portraying rasheeda 
moore as a vengeful exlover who trapped the mayor in an fbi sting 
operation because he had abandoned her for another woman 
moore a former model denied the suggestion friday at the 
mayors cocaine and perjury trial insisting i was not out to 
