the following is an overview of the process 
involved in making the powerful west german mark east germanys 
legal tender on sunday 
the west german bundesbank transported 25 billion marks 151 
billion to 13 state banks in east germany the currency amounts 
to 600 tons of paper money 400 million individual bills worth 
about 243 billion marks and 500 million coins worth about 700 
million marks 
