circulation the public will be asked to return remaining cash by 
friday and it will be counted and stored pending destruction 
depending on a persons age all private savings accounts of up 
to 2000 marks or 1200 4000 marks or 2400 and 6000 marks 
or 3600 will be exchanged at a rate of 1 west german mark to 1 
